The '''Thelvin Order''' was a society founded on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Barundi]]. Their purpose and organization seemed unclear, but they were known to have their own language which was unique to their people and followers. At some point, several [[Barundi (species)|Barundi]] natives were taken from the planet and placed on an uncharted world where they were set to guard the [[Yavin Vassilika]]. When [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunters]] arrived to claim the artifact, they noticed that the natives still spoke in the language of the Thelvin Order of Barundi.

